==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hesitancy
<hw>Hes"i*tan*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>haesitantia</ets> a stammering.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
hesitating, or pausing to consider; slowness in deciding; vacillation;
also, the manner of one who hesitates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A stammering; a faltering in speech.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hesitant</ent>⟦br⟧
